34
00:04:03,243 --> 00:04:05,411
<i>Aku juga harus berlatih menuruni gunung.</i>

35
00:04:05,995 --> 00:04:08,039
<i>Jika tak mau mati di Seleksi Akhir,</i>

36
00:04:08,122 --> 00:04:09,290
<i>aku harus berlatih keras.</i>

37
00:04:13,753 --> 00:04:16,547
<i>Seiring aku berlatih berlari
menuruni gunung tiap hari,</i>

38
00:04:16,965 --> 00:04:19,759
<i>aku semakin cakap menghindari
perangkap dan lubang jebakan.</i>

39
00:04:20,593 --> 00:04:22,679
<i>Karena kekuatan fisikku meningkat,</i>

40
