73
00:06:42,652 --> 00:06:44,153
<i>Aku menggunakan katanaku</i>

74
00:06:44,529 --> 00:06:47,031
<i>dan menerjang Pak Urokodaki.</i>

75
00:06:47,448 --> 00:06:51,369
<i>Sementara Pak Urokodaki
tak bersenjata dan tanpa pelindung.</i>

76
00:06:54,205 --> 00:06:56,499
<i>Tapi dia sangat kuat.</i>

77
00:06:57,041 --> 00:07:00,837
<i>Aku terus dijatuhkan olehnya.</i>

78
00:07:05,842 --> 00:07:07,593
Kakak pulang, Nezuko.

79
00:07:17,854 --> 00:07:21,482
<i>Hari ini, aku belajar teknik pernapasan
dan Gaya Bernapas.</i>

80
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,527
